snippet.title: Happy Little Trees 002: Encouragement and Inspiration with guest, artist Amber Kenney
snippet.description:
This week we have Adam's wife, Amber Kenney, an artist who finds inspiration everywhere. They talk about what it's like to encourage others in their artwork, whether it's better to wait for inspiration or seek it out, what kind of basic information is helpful for better brushwork, and where Amber's love for art has led her. 
Podcast audio also available everywhere - (Spotify, iTunes, etc)
Website: https://www.adamkenneyart.com
Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/happylittletrees
Instagram: @adamkenneyart
Contact: adamkenneyart@gmail.com
